WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
The gunship was so far away that it could be heard as if it were a bean.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
The bullets sometimes made a sound like a fire and passed through the field.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
When I approached the forest, I saw many black shadows moving in the forest.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.000
