00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:56.000
He said that they came with him.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
I asked where he was, but he was very worried and was looking around,

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
so he said he didn't know where he was.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:08.000
I wanted to see him, so I looked all over the place, but I couldn't find him.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:13.000
I was tired, and I thought I could see him when the night came, so I decided to sleep.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:16.000
I didn't know what time it was.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
