00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.000
I could smell the faint smell of blood.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:42.000
The bedding was hanging on the ground wall, and I took it out.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:48.000
I put it on a box that had many of them nearby, and I fell asleep on it.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:51.000
I felt like I was lying down after a long time.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:54.000
A cold wind came and swept my cheeks.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.000
I said, Mother, you were alive.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:01:59.000
I went. Thank you.

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:03.000
